/etc/udev/rules.d/10-elite.rules
SYSFS{idVendor}=="04d8", SYSFS{idProduct}=="000a", RUN+="/sbin/modprobe -q ftdi_sio vendor=0x04d8 product=0x000a"
sudo apt-get install python3-serial python3-websockets python3-dotenv python3-netifaces
python3 socket-server.py

EMERGENCY STOP a LOCO is NOT supported on the elite. So do not set a deceleration profile on the decoder! You will need to control deceleration manually.